Broccoli Tarts

Crust:
1/4 c almond flour
1 tsp flax seed meal
2 tbsp water

Filling:
1/8 c chopped broccoli florets
1/2 oz feta cheese
1 egg white

Preheat oven to 400F. Combine ingredients for dough. Once incorporated, knead dough until it holds its shape. Press dough into tart molds. Brush the crusts with the egg white.
Add broccoli and feta. Bake for 7 min. Finish by broiling for 2 min. Makes 3 mini tarts.
